# ANIMATION SYSTEM RULES (FacePe)

## Style

- **Personality:** calm, premium, confident—**never playful**.
- **Philosophy:** motion **confirms** interaction and **reveals** content once; no ambient loops.

## Allowed

- **Fade up:** `opacity` + `translateY(12px)` max; duration **`280–320ms`**.
- **Fade in:** opacity only, **`150–200ms`** for icons.
- **Hover lift (cards):** `translateY(-2px)` **`duration-md`** **`ease-premium`**.
- **Hover (primary button):** subtle `brightness-110` or `translateY(0.5px)` — pick **one** project-wide.
- **Link chevron:** `translateX(2px)` on hover, **`150ms`**.
- **Stagger:** `60–100ms` between cards, max **6** nodes.

## Scroll

- Prefer **`IntersectionObserver`** toggling a class `.is-inview` over per-frame JS.
- **GSAP:** allowed for **one** staggered reveal per page section family (e.g. product grid); use `once: true` behavior.

## Durations (Tailwind tokens)

- Use **`duration-fast`** (`150ms`), **`duration-md`** (`300ms`), **`duration-slow`** (`480ms`) from `tailwind.config.js` instead of ad-hoc ms values in class strings.

## Easing

- Default: **`ease-premium`** (`tailwind.config.js`) → `cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1)` for entrances and hovers.

## Performance

- Only animate **`transform`** and **`opacity`**.
- No `transition-all`—always list properties.

## Reduced motion

- Honor `prefers-reduced-motion: reduce` — skip stagger; show final state.

## DO NOT

- Bounce / elastic easing.
- Parallax text or background grids.
- Rotate logos or CTA pills.
- Animate blur filters on large sections.
